<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style="font-family: arial;"><div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><div><font face="arial" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>You recently got in touch to make a change to your policy. In order to action this change, we had to cancel your original policy and re-set this up with your requested amends - as a result of this,&nbsp;<b>you are owed a refund</b>.</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><b>Your refund</b><br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>As you paid in a single payment, a pro-rata refund of&nbsp;<i>£XXX</i>&nbsp;will appear in the account from which you originally paid in the next 3 to 10 working days.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>If you have any further queries, please feel free to contact us on&nbsp;<b>01242 808740</b>.<br></span><font face="arial" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></font><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E:&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</a><br><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
